             sworn.</p>
               <p>I was sent for to take up the prisoner 
               <persName id="t17890603-39-person362">
                  Samuel
                   Wright
               <interp inst="t17890603-39-person362" type="surname" value="Wright"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17890603-39-person362" type="given" value="Samuel"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17890603-39-person362" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             in St. Paul's Church-yard, by order of the prosecutor, I took them before the Alderman.</p>
               <p>Court to Hall. Where was that piece of callico that you now produce? - It only came in an hour or two before the robbery, the value of it is something more than it is laid in the indictment.</p>
               <p>PRISONER BATES's DEFENCE.</p>
               <p>I was hired by another man to carry it into Old-street; I know nothing of this lad at all, and the man was gone.</p>
